<problem>


<p>Which of the following is <math>tan(theta)/(sec(theta) - cos(theta))</math> equal to?</p>


<!--*********************************************
            User solution input
**********************************************-->  
<p><answer name="ans1" shuffleOrder>
  <choice credit="1"><math>csc(theta)</math></choice>
  <choice><math>sin(theta)/(1 + cos(theta))</math></choice>
  <choice><math>sin(theta)</math></choice>
  <choice><math>tan(theta)/(1 - cos^2 (theta))</math></choice>
</answer>
</p>

